Simplified Clue game engine: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cluedo

Explanation on implementations: Solving Cluedo.pdf

Usage:
clue.py then player types separated by comma.
Player types are:
h - human player
r - random player
p - planning player
bn - the first BN player - bn can only be played with 3 players total, and only as the first player
bn2 - the second BN player

The rooms are described are numbers:
Where: 1 - Study; 2 - Hall; 3 - Lounge; 4 - DinningRoom; 5 - Kitchen;
6 - BallRoom; 7 - Conservatory; 8 - BilliardRoom; 9 - Library

